		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You point and whisper your message at the target. It alone hears the message and may reply in a whisper audible only to you. However the voice that your message is delivered in sounds like a creature of your choosing that you have heard at least once.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You may cast this spell through solid objects even if you cannot see your target. However it is blocked by 3ft of soil, 1ft of stone, or 1 inch of metal. It passes through doors and around corners with ease.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Deception and Perform checks made to trick the target of the Missage spell gain advantage.</p>",
